OL,3,CPolice officers sacked over
OL,4,Cdiscriminatory whatsapp messages
OL,6,FEight West Yorkshire Police officers
OL,7,Fhave been barred from policing over a
OL,8,FWhatsApp group featuring routine
OL,9,Fmisogyny and casual racism.
OL,11,FThe Pudsey-based officers were found
OL,12,Fguilty of gross misconduct over
OL,13,Fderogatory, offensive and
OL,14,Fdiscriminatory messages posted in the
OL,15,Fgroup between August 2020 and November
OL,16,F2021.
