OL,6,FThe hearing panel, chaired by the
OL,7,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,8,F(IOPC), found that all five serving
OL,9,Fofficers should be dismissed and that
OL,10,Fthe three officers who resigned while
OL,11,Funder investigation would have been
OL,12,Fdismissed if still serving.
OL,14,FA panel heard how the officers shared
OL,15,Fphotographs of death scenes, car
OL,16,Fcrashes, missing people and detainees
OL,17,Fand that the group was characterised
OL,18,Fby "mean-spirited and bullying remarks
OL,19,Fabout colleagues and members of the
OL,20,Fpublic".
