OL,6,FThe officers that have been barred are
OL,7,FPC Luke Riddett, Ex-PC Tom Harrison,
OL,8,FPS Mark Otter, PC Javaid Habebb, Ex-PC
OL,9,FMatthew Harrison, PC Dominique
OL,10,FHawkins, Ex-PC Lee Hillyard and PC X
OL,11,F(who is subject of an anonymity order).
OL,13,FAll eight will now be added to the
OL,14,FCollege of Policing's Barred List
OL,15,Fpreventing them from gaining any
OL,16,Ffurther employment in policing.
