OL,6,FThe disciplinary panel found a total
OL,7,Fof 67 allegations proven at the level
OL,8,Fof gross misconduct, a further 38
OL,9,Fproven at the level of misconduct and
OL,10,F20 allegations were found not proven.
OL,12,FWithin the group PC Luke Riddett
OL,13,Fshared a photograph of a bearded Asian
OL,14,Fdetainee with the caption "if you had
OL,15,Fto draw a terrorist..."
