OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent Tanya
OL,7,FWilkins, Head of West Yorkshire
OL,8,FPolice's Professional Standards
OL,9,FDirectorate, said: "This misconduct
OL,10,Fhearing looked not only at the actions
OL,11,Fof this group but also their inaction.
OL,12,FThe lack of challenge and complicity
OL,13,Fof a supervisor being involved in
OL,14,Fthese conversations has allowed a
OL,15,Fculture of routine misogyny, casual
OL,16,Fracism and bullying to develop within
OL,17,Fthis team.
