OL,6,F"We make clear to all employees of
OL,7,FWest Yorkshire Police the standards we
OL,8,Fexpect of them both on and off duty
OL,9,Fand have a specific policy in place
OL,10,Faround the use of social media, which
OL,11,Fincludes WhatsApp. The messages that
OL,12,Fwere looked at as part of this
OL,13,Finvestigation were mean-spirited and
OL,14,Fnot representative of the inclusive
OL,15,Fculture we seek to foster in West
OL,16,FYorkshire Police.
