OL,6,FThe IOPC found that some of the
OL,7,Fofficers interviewed as part of the
OL,8,Finvestigation said the use of
OL,9,FWhatsApp, while against force policy,
OL,10,Fwas encouraged by some sergeants.
OL,12,FThey also added that several officers
OL,13,Fsaid they used "dark humour" as a way
OL,14,Fto deal with difficult situations and
OL,15,Fsome said this was actively encouraged
OL,16,Fduring their initial training.
