OL,3,CPolice officers sacked over
OL,4,Cdiscriminatory whatsapp messages
OL,6,FFollowing the investigation West
OL,7,FYorkshire Police said it is rolling
OL,8,Fout new handheld devices to officers,
OL,9,Fwhich would include an alternative app
OL,10,Fallowing officers to share messages
OL,11,Finstantly among teams, without needing
OL,12,Fto use their personal devices.
OL,14,FThe force also says it has taken steps
OL,15,Fto address the issues identified
OL,16,Fincluding reviewing training and
OL,17,Fpolicies around social media use, with
OL,18,Fa focus on workplace behaviour and
OL,19,Fculture.
